channel.title: Looking for a dev [PI]
channel.description:
Hi. I'm fairly new at PI 317, but i know the basics so.. [size=7pt]yay[/size] I'm looking for a team to join or maybe if someone is willing to join me with the PI Project.
The reason why i want to join a team is because i'm interested to learn java coding on RSPS.
I know, i know. I'm not really talented at coding but i'll be able to advertise, make youtube videos and handle the rsps website.
Just comment your skype and i'll make sure to add you. :D
